<h1>Maxbot interface</h1>

<p><em>A <a href="https://www.sinatrarb.com">Sinatra</a> site that shares a database with a <a href="https://github.com/cinchrb/cinch">Cinch</a></em>Ruby IRC Bot</p>

<p>The bot is currently running in the ##codeunion and #appacad-sf-aug4-2014 channels on Freenode. You can go to <a href="www.kiwiirc.com">KiwiIRC</a> to access IRC in your browser. </p>

<p>You can view the code for this project (the IRC Bot and the Sinatra site) <a href="https://github.com/maxpleaner/maxbot">on GitHub.</a></p>

