<h3>How to use the bot on IRC</h3>

<h4>"!echo" - Type !echo followed by anything you want and the bot will repeat it back to you.</h4>

<p>  
  <em>Example:</em><br>
  macsplean1: !echo I want you to repeat this back to me <br>
  maxbot: macsplean1 said "I want you to repeat this back to me"
</p>

<h4>"!log" - Type !log to make a note that you can view on this site </h4>

<p>
  <em>Example:</em> <br> 
  macsplean1: !log record me <br>
  maxbot: Message from macsplean1 was logged - see it at maxbot.ngrok.com <br>
</p>

<p>You can also optionally include a topic with your log</p>
  <em>Example:</em><br>
  macsplean1: !log t=test_topic This message will be categorized as test_topic <br>
  maxbot: Message from macsplean1 was logged - see it at maxbot.ngrok.com <br>
  <em>(At this point, each post can only have one tag and tags cannot have spaces) </em>

